The specimen is similar to
Libumella athabascensis Green, 1963
from the Mississippian of the Rocky Mountains, Canada ( Green 1963 ; Crasquin 1985 ) and from the Late Permian of South China (
Yuan et al. 2007
). Nevertheless, it differs by the presence of a nodule in the dorso-median part of the carapace.
